This paper deals with cooperative communications in wireless body area networks, which involves signal processing, information theory, and network infrastructure. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.IT (Information Theory), followed by cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture), cs.MA (Multiagent Systems), cs.SY (Systems and Control), and cs.LG (Machine Learning).
